  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Puppet Masters who practice the Blue Technique are known as Warmasters. The traditional puppeteering styles call upon Puppet Masters to invest fully in their puppets for offense and protection, whilst the puppeteer themselves cowers away. </p><p>Warmasters share a great disdain for these tactics and instead fight alongside their puppets. They lead the way to victory and the Puppets follow behind, not the other way around. Some follow the Blue Technique to evolve a renowned practice from a mindset of cowardice, whilst others invest in the technique to make battle exciting.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
